{"tid":2042634,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本女星31歲仍與爸爸共浴同睡一床　自爆太愛單親爸︰我像他女友","createTime":"2020-05-30T02:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T05:28:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"46fc57f0fcd0970a101be26fec0ef500dfc530c3","tid":2042634,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:39:43.000Z","msg":"日本家庭有母女共浴的習慣，但成年女兒與爸爸共浴就可免則免。一名31歲日本女星，日前上綜藝節目時自爆，至今仍與64歲的單親爸爸共浴、同睡一床；最近爸爸再婚，更有感自己像他的前女友。言論一出，即時引起網民譁然，「完全像犯罪。」<br />\n<br />\n據日本傳媒報道，日本綜藝節目《有吉反省會》每集邀請都藝人嘉賓講自身故事，並反省不足之處。在5月23日播出的一集中，性感寫真女星如月Saya就訴說自己與單親爸爸的親密關係。<br />\n<br />\n如月Saya不時在社交平台分享性感照和生活點滴，當中有些是疑似「放閃」照，例如她躺在床上準備入睡，隱約見到身旁有神祕男子頭部；又有一張與神祕男子飲酒的照片，令外界以為她結交了秘密男友。<br />\n<br />\n爸爸再婚 自己就像前度<br />\n她在節目中解畫稱，相中的神秘男其實是她的爸爸，自己和爸爸一直都維持單身。現年31歲的她自爆過於喜歡爸爸，至今仍會和爸爸一同洗澡，甚至睡在同一張床上。不過，最近爸爸再婚後，就有感自己像變成他的前女友。<br />\n<br />\n主持人聞言感到訝異，但未有批評，只回應「真是開放的家庭氛圍」、「喜歡爸爸沒什麼好反省」。<br />\n<br />\n隱瞞爸爸做性感寫真偶像<br />\n不過，如月Saya也擔心節目出街後會惹爸爸生氣，影響父女關係，因爸爸是個很認真嚴肅的人，所以她一直對爸爸謊稱，自己現從事全職配音員，隱瞞是性感寫真偶像一事。<br />\n<br />\n節目播出後引起網民爭議，認為如月Saya的行為明顯異常。「31歲女兒仍與爸爸共浴睡覺，完全像犯罪。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2655000/2656184/japan_thumb_20200529_ch_v2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2655000%2F2656184%2Fjapan_thumb_20200529_ch_v2_1024.jpg&h=9b4fa414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2655000/2656184/japan_girl_07_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2655000%2F2656184%2Fjapan_girl_07_1024.jpg&h=809179e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2655000/2656184/japan_girl_08_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2655000%2F2656184%2Fjapan_girl_08_1024.jpg&h=a7e1acdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f7afb759b34b0d16f8b0968e2ee4aea23f94c38","tid":2042634,"uid":182334,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"個樣都安全嘅"},{"pid":"ede2172c1a87b9cd620b16525611bce84937d8d6","tid":2042634,"uid":20809,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"其實有乜問題，都31歲人，有個人思考能力，甚至係愛上佢老豆有埋性行為都冇問題<br />\n同性戀都係咁"},{"pid":"8cbf22fc2cf13ce8e7a920aa6923c9789d79d861","tid":2042634,"uid":126590,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:45:39.000Z","msg":"爸爸會唔會忍得好辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahsUBwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahsUBwt.jpg&h=6c36173d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UohUBwu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUohUBwu.jpg&h=121f93a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdUjNC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDdUjNC9.jpg&h=28acdfdd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c901c1f599922214eb222f7f8b343f5f1824466","tid":2042634,"uid":141164,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"實有做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3812d6b479daffbe10b42b1ee974ef332617bf6","tid":2042634,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f7afb759b34b0d16f8b0968e2ee4aea23f94c38","tid":2042634,"uid":182334,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"個樣都安全嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"有咁差咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b2118264b542472f5a77953f22396b737aa51b","tid":2042634,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0